インタフェース IContainerListener

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    AnvilScreen, CreativeCraftingListener, FakePlayer, ServerPlayerEntity

    public interface IContainerListener

    • メソッドのサマリー

    • メソッドの詳細

      • sendAllContents

        void sendAllContents(Container containerToSend,
                     NonNullList<ItemStack> itemsList)
        update the crafting window inventory with the items in the list

      • sendSlotContents

        void sendSlotContents(Container containerToSend,
                      int slotInd,
                      ItemStack stack)
        Sends the contents of an inventory slot to the client-side Container. This doesn't have to match the actual contents of that slot.

      • sendWindowProperty

        void sendWindowProperty(Container containerIn,
                        int varToUpdate,
                        int newValue)
        Sends two ints to the client-side Container. Used for furnace burning time, smelting progress, brewing progress, and enchanting level. Normally the first int identifies which variable to update, and the second contains the new value. Both are truncated to shorts in non-local SMP.
